snippet.title: Shin'en: The Punchuin (Nintendo Switch) Trailer
snippet.description:
http://thepunchuin.shinen.com
Follow @ShinenGames on Twitter for the latest news!
Release: 20 December 2022

Punch your way to the treasure of the mountain in THE PUNCHUIN!

You are on a quest to solve the mystery of the treasure of Punch Mountain. Punch your way down, collect money and diamonds, improve your punching skills and make some new friends along the way.
